room_title: Escape room "Revive & Survive" by Escape Room Dilemma in York
room_description:
The overlord of the foreign race has gathered a team of the most brilliant minds the earth has to offer with hopes of regenerating the imperial commander and his only heir to their race.
You will be given 1 hour to use the equipment provided in order to restore the life-force of the Chosen or you and your world will suffer the same fate as many worlds beforeâ€¦ Will you be able to Revive in order to Survive?
